| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2538 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5d860937-0f38-5953-b445-ae9f0ffb20b3"
